Package: yarrr
Title: A companion package to YaRrr! The Pirate’s Guide to R
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: “Nathaniel Phillips <yarrr.book@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: This package contains a mixture of functions and datasets referred to in the introductory e-book YaRrr! The Pirate’s Guide to R (the latest version of the e-book is available for free here: https://goo.gl/tbPP9K). See http://nathanieldphillips.com/yarrr for additional information.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.3)
License: What license is it under?
LazyData: true
Suggests: plyr, dplyr,RColorBrewer
